---
/**
 * V1: TERMINAL — CRT/Hacker aesthetic
 * Scanlines, phosphor glow, monospace everything, markdown syntax decorators
 */
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <title>Ethan Reimann – Terminal</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap');

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0a0e14;
      --fg: #b3b1ad;
      --green: #7fd962;
      --cyan: #39bae6;
      --amber: #e6b450;
      --red: #f07178;
      --dim: #454b54;
      --glow: 0 0 8px rgba(127, 217, 98, 0.3);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
      font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 0.75rem + 0.5vw, 1.05rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* CRT Scanlines */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 10000;
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          0deg,
          transparent,
          transparent 1px,
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 1px,
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 2px
        );
    }

    /* CRT vignette */
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 60%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 100%);
    }

    ::selection { background: var(--green); color: var(--bg); }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 72ch;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2ch;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2em 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dim);
    }
    .site-title {
      font-size: 1em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--green);
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
    }
    .site-title a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav { display: flex; gap: 2ch; list-style: none; }
    .nav a {
      color: var(--cyan);
      text-decoration: none;
      position: relative;
    }
    .nav a::before { content: '['; color: var(--dim); }
    .nav a::after { content: ']'; color: var(--dim); }
    .nav a:hover { color: var(--green); text-shadow: var(--glow); }

    /* Prompt line */
    .prompt { color: var(--dim); }
    .prompt-user { color: var(--green); text-shadow: var(--glow); }
    .prompt-path { color: var(--cyan); }
    .prompt-symbol { color: var(--amber); }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      padding: 3em 0 2em;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dim);
    }
    .hero-ascii {
      color: var(--green);
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
      font-size: clamp(0.45rem, 0.3rem + 0.8vw, 0.85rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      white-space: pre;
      overflow: hidden;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      margin-top: 1em;
      color: var(--dim);
    }
    .hero-sub span { color: var(--amber); }

    /* Sections */
    section { padding: 2em 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dim); }
    section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1em;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--amber);
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    h2::before { content: '## '; color: var(--dim); }

    /* About */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
      gap: 3ch;
      align-items: start;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .about-text .comment { color: var(--dim); }
    .portrait {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: var(--dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--dim);
      filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.2) brightness(0.8);
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* GitHub */
    .github-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6em 2em;
      border: 1px solid var(--green);
      color: var(--green);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .github-link:hover {
      background: var(--green);
      color: var(--bg);
      text-shadow: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(127, 217, 98, 0.3);
    }

    /* Callout */
    .callout {
      background: rgba(127, 217, 98, 0.05);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
      padding: 1.5em 2ch;
      color: var(--fg);
    }
    .callout strong { color: var(--green); }

    /* Lists */
    ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    li { padding-left: 3ch; position: relative; }
    li::before { content: '> '; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--dim); }
    li em { color: var(--amber); font-style: italic; }

    /* Blog */
    .blog-entry {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2ch;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .blog-date { color: var(--dim); flex-shrink: 0; white-space: nowrap; }
    .blog-title a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; }
    .blog-title a:hover { color: var(--green); text-shadow: var(--glow); }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      padding: 2em 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--dim);
      color: var(--dim);
      text-align: right;
    }
    .footer a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer a:hover { color: var(--green); }

    /* Cursor blink */
    .cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 0.6em;
      height: 1.1em;
      background: var(--green);
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
      animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }
    @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

    /* Back link */
    .back { position: fixed; top: 1em; right: 2em; z-index: 100000; }
    .back a {
      color: var(--dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    }
    .back a:hover { color: var(--green); }

    /* Fade in */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .fade { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
    .fade-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .fade-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .fade-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .fade-4 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .fade-5 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .fade-6 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
    .fade-7 { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
    .fade-8 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="back"><a href="/">← versions</a></div>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <header class="header fade">
      <h1 class="site-title"><a href="/v1/">ethan_reimann</a></h1>
      <nav>
        <ul class="nav">
          <li><a href="/photography/">photography</a></li>
          <li><a href="/projects/">projects</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero fade fade-1">
      <div class="hero-ascii" aria-label="EthanReimann.com">
 _____ _   _                 ____      _
| ____| |_| |__   __ _ _ __ |  _ \ ___(_)_ __ ___   __ _ _ __  _ __    ___ ___  _ __ ___
|  _| | __| '_ \ / _` | '_ \| |_) / _ \ | '_ ` _ \ / _` | '_ \| '_ \  / __/ _ \| '_ ` _ \
| |___| |_| | | | (_| | | | |  _ &lt;  __/ | | | | | | (_| | | | | | | || (_| (_) | | | | | |
|_____|\__|_| |_|\__,_|_| |_|_| \_\___|_|_| |_| |_|\__,_|_| |_|_| |_(_)___\___/|_| |_| |_|</div>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        <span class="prompt-user">ethan</span><span class="prompt">@</span><span class="prompt-path">web</span>
        <span class="prompt-symbol"> $ </span>
        cat about.txt<span class="cursor"></span>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-grid fade fade-2" style="padding: 2em 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dim);">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="comment">// Hello World!</p>
        <br />
        <p>
          This is one of my many attempts at a website in this modern world
          where personal websites are very uncommon. My name is none other than
          Ethan Reimann, a 10th grade student in the United States. You can find
          me and my work all across the internet, everything from YouTube videos
          to contributions to various GitHub projects.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a class="github-link" href="https://github.com/ReimannLabs">~/github</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <img class="portrait" src="/portrait.jpg" alt="Ethan Reimann" width="200" height="267" />
    </section>

    <section class="fade fade-3">
      <div class="callout">
        <strong>Why Have a Personal Website in the 2020s?</strong><br />
        Personal websites have always felt like a lost art to me. This site shall
        grow with time, as I find the time. In all honesty, I would rather my
        work be on a website owned by me rather than some billionaire social
        media platform.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="fade fade-4">
      <h2>Recent Books I've Read</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>The Brothers Karamazov — Fyodor Dostoevsky — <em>Currently Reading</em></li>
        <li>The Giver — Lois Lowry</li>
        <li>We Who Wrestle with God — Jordan Peterson</li>
        <li>Welcome to the Universe — Neil DeGrasse Tyson, Et al.</li>
        <li>Ghost Town Living — Brent Underwood</li>
        <li>Too Big to Fail — Andrew Sorkin</li>
        <li>The Order of Time — Carlo Rovelli</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="fade fade-5">
      <h2>(Some of) My Favorite Albums</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>I'm The Problem — Morgan Wallen</li>
        <li>From A Room: Volume 2 — Chris Stapleton</li>
        <li>Chief — Eric Church</li>
        <li>Leather — Cody Johnson</li>
        <li>From Elvis in Memphis — Elvis Presley</li>
        <li>What Are We Waiting For? — For King &amp; Country</li>
        <li>Jars of Clay — Jars of Clay</li>
        <li>Summertime Blues — Zach Bryan</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="fade fade-6">
      <div class="callout">
        <strong>What I Write About on "The Blog"</strong><br />
        There is no set purpose for my blog, I will likely treat it as a digital
        public journal. Posts will be written at random, and topics will be,
        well, also, random.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="fade fade-7">
      <h2>The Blog</h2>
      <div class="blog-entry">
        <time class="blog-date" datetime="2025-10-25">2025-10-25</time>
        <div class="blog-title"><a href="/a-new-start/">A New Start</a></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer fade fade-8">
      <p>Powered by <a href="https://reimannlabs.com/">Reimann Labs</a></p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
